OL,3,CFifa to investigate Argentina's World
OL,4,CCup final conduct, reports say
OL,6,FFifa will reportedly investigate
OL,7,FArgentina's post-match conduct
OL,8,Ffollowing a sore World Cup final
OL,9,Fdefeat to newly-crowned champions
OL,10,FSpain, according to the Press
OL,11,FAssociation (PA).
OL,13,FRodrigo Hernandez lifted the trophy
OL,14,Fwith pride as his team touched down in
OL,15,FMadrid, following a tense 1-0 win
OL,16,Fagainst Argentina at the MetLife
OL,17,FStadium in New Jersey.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
