OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1784620076
OL,3,CFifa to investigate Argentina's World
OL,4,CCup final conduct, reports say
OL,6,FHowever, amongst the post-match
OL,7,Fcelebrations there were signs of
OL,8,Faggression on the pitch from the
OL,9,Fopposition on Sunday night.
OL,11,FFifa is will internally investigate
OL,12,FArgentina's conduct after violence
OL,13,Ferupted following the final whistle of
OL,14,Fthe World Cup Final, PA understands.
OL,16,FDuring the match, Leandro Paredes was
OL,17,Fshown a red card for violent conduct
OL,18,Fafter grabbing and pushing Spain
OL,19,Fplayers - including Eric Garcia and
OL,20,FGavi.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
