OL,3,CFifa to investigate Argentina's World
OL,4,CCup final conduct, reports say
OL,6,FNahuel Molina attempted to knock over
OL,7,FRodri while the Manchester City
OL,8,Fmidfielder was celebrating Spain's win.
OL,10,FEnzo Fernandez was sent off with two
OL,11,Fyellow cards in 10 minutes after an
OL,12,Faltercation with the referee and for
OL,13,Fcolliding with Spain's Pau Cubarsi.
OL,15,FAnd, in an even more surprising turn
OL,16,Fof events, Argentina coach Roberto
OL,17,FAyala appeared to try to punch Spain's
OL,18,FDani Olmo in the face.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
