OL,3,CFifa to investigate Argentina's World
OL,4,CCup final conduct, reports say
OL,6,FThe entire Argentina side turned their
OL,7,Fback on the trophy celebration while
OL,8,FSpain lifted the World Cup.
OL,10,FAccording to PA, the match
OL,11,Fcommissioner's report will be reviewed
OL,12,Fwithin FIFA before they decide whether
OL,13,Fto proceed with a disciplinary against
OL,14,Fa player, and possibly the Argentinian
OL,15,FFA (AFA).
OL,17,FITV News has approached Fifa for a
OL,18,Fstatement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
