OL,3,CFifa to investigate Argentina's World
OL,4,CCup final conduct, reports say
OL,6,FIt is still not known whether Fifa is
OL,7,Finvestigating Argentinian players
OL,8,Fafter they held up a banner expressing
OL,9,FArgentinian sovereignty over the
OL,10,FFalkland Islands following their semi-
OL,11,Ffinal win against England.
OL,13,FThis goes against tournament
OL,14,Fregulations, and in the 2024 Euros,
OL,15,Fone-match bans were imposed on Spain's
OL,16,FRodri and Alvaro Morata after they
OL,17,Fchanted about Spain's claims to
OL,18,FGibraltar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
