OL,3,CFifa to investigate Argentina's World
OL,4,CCup final conduct, reports say
OL,6,FThis is only the second time, after a
OL,7,F2010 victory in South Africa, that
OL,8,FSpain has won the World Cup title.
OL,10,FThey successfully managed to dethrone
OL,11,Fthree-times-champion Argentina 1-0 in
OL,12,FEast Rutherford, New Jersey.
